{"title":"Docker安装Kafka","date":"2020-05-07T19:01:58.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"May 8, 2020","L":"05/08/2020","MM-DD":"05-08"},"link":"2020/05/08/docker-install-kafka","tags":["Docker","Kafka"],"categories":["Kafka"],"updated":"2020-05-17T04:22:52.086Z","content":"<h2 id=\"kafka\">kafka<a title=\"#kafka\" href=\"#kafka\"></a></h2>\n<h3 id=\"下载zookeeper镜像\">下载zookeeper镜像<a title=\"#下载zookeeper镜像\" href=\"#下载zookeeper镜像\"></a></h3>\n<p>kafka需要zookeeper管理，所以需要先安装zookeeper。可以下载官方的<code>zookeeper</code>或者<code>wurstmeister/zookeeper</code>版本，建议下载<code>wurstmeister/zookeeper</code>，kafka也是选择的<code>wurstmeister/kafka</code>版本</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">docker pull zookeeper:latest</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>or</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">docker pull wurstmeister/zookeeper:latest</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h3 id=\"运行zookeeper容器\">运行zookeeper容器<a title=\"#运行zookeeper容器\" href=\"#运行zookeeper容器\"></a></h3>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">docker run --name zookeeper -p 2181:2181 -d zookeeper</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>or</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">docker run --name zookeeper -p 2181:2181 -d wurstmeister/zookeeper</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h3 id=\"下载kafka镜像\">下载kafka镜像<a title=\"#下载kafka镜像\" href=\"#下载kafka镜像\"></a></h3>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">docker pull wurstmeister/kafka:latest</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h3 id=\"运行kafka容器\">运行kafka容器<a title=\"#运行kafka容器\" href=\"#运行kafka容器\"></a></h3>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">docker run -t -d --name kafka -p 9092:9092 \\</span><br><span class=\"line\">    -e KAFKA_BROKER_ID=0 \\</span><br><span class=\"line\">    -e KAFKA_ZOOKEEPER_CONNECT=192.168.222.133:2181 \\</span><br><span class=\"line\">    -e KAFKA_ADVERTISED_LISTENERS=PLAINTEXT://192.168.222.133:9092 \\</span><br><span class=\"line\">    -e KAFKA_LISTENERS=PLAINTEXT://0.0.0.0:9092 \\</span><br><span class=\"line\">    wurstmeister/kafka</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>这里主要设置4个参数</p>\n<ul>\n<li><code>-e KAFKA_BROKER_ID=0</code> 在kafka集群中，每个kafka都有一个BROKER_ID来区分自己</li>\n<li><code>-e KAFKA_ZOOKEEPER_CONNECT=192.168.222.133:2181/kafka</code> 配置zookeeper管理kafka的路径</li>\n<li><code>-e KAFKA_ADVERTISED_LISTENERS=PLAINTEXT://192.168.222.133:9092</code> 把kafka的地址端口注册给zookeeper</li>\n<li><code>-e KAFKA_LISTENERS=PLAINTEXT://0.0.0.0:9092</code> 配置kafka的监听端口</li>\n</ul>\n<blockquote>\n<p>第2点和第3点的ip换成服务器ip<br>\n代码后面还可以加上<code>-v /etc/localtime:/etc/localtime</code>用于指定容器时间同步虚拟机的时间</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h3 id=\"进入kafka容器\">进入kafka容器<a title=\"#进入kafka容器\" href=\"#进入kafka容器\"></a></h3>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">docker <span class=\"built_in\">exec</span> -it kafka /bin/bash</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h3 id=\"进入所在目录\">进入所在目录<a title=\"#进入所在目录\" href=\"#进入所在目录\"></a></h3>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">cd</span> opt/kafka_2.12_2.5.0/bin</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<blockquote>\n<p>kafka的版本根据不同时期可能有所不同，可以先通过<code>cd opt</code>，然后通过<code>ls</code>命令查看kafka当前版本。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"kafka管理器\">kafka管理器<a title=\"#kafka管理器\" href=\"#kafka管理器\"></a></h2>\n<h3 id=\"安装kafka-manager\">安装kafka-manager<a title=\"#安装kafka-manager\" href=\"#安装kafka-manager\"></a></h3>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">docker pull sheepkiller/kafka-manager:latest</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h3 id=\"运行kafka-manager\">运行kafka-manager<a title=\"#运行kafka-manager\" href=\"#运行kafka-manager\"></a></h3>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">docker run -d --name kafka-manager \\</span><br><span class=\"line\">    --link zookeeper:zookeeper \\</span><br><span class=\"line\">    --link kafka:kafka -p 9000:9000 \\</span><br><span class=\"line\">    --restart=always \\</span><br><span class=\"line\">    --env ZK_HOSTS=zookeeper:2181 \\</span><br><span class=\"line\">    sheepkiller/kafka-manager</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h2 id=\"相关链接\">相关链接<a title=\"#相关链接\" href=\"#相关链接\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://blog.csdn.net/weixin_40910372/article/details/103962237\" title=\"docker安装kafka和zookeeper\" target=\"_blank\">docker安装kafka和zookeeper</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.jianshu.com/p/e8c29cba9fae\" title=\"docker安装kafka\" target=\"_blank\">docker安装kafka</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.cnblogs.com/Jacian/p/11421114.html\" title=\"Docker搭建Zookeeper&amp;Kafka集群\" target=\"_blank\">Docker搭建Zookeeper&amp;Kafka集群</a></li>\n</ul>\n","prev":{"title":"Docker安装teamcity","link":"2020/05/13/docker-install-teamcity"},"next":{"title":"Hexo生成github page","link":"2020/04/29/hexo-generate-github-page"},"plink":"http://blog.arytry.com/2020/05/08/docker-install-kafka/","toc":[{"id":"kafka","title":"kafka","index":"1","children":[{"id":"下载zookeeper镜像","title":"下载zookeeper镜像","index":"1.1"},{"id":"运行zookeeper容器","title":"运行zookeeper容器","index":"1.2"},{"id":"下载kafka镜像","title":"下载kafka镜像","index":"1.3"},{"id":"运行kafka容器","title":"运行kafka容器","index":"1.4"},{"id":"进入kafka容器","title":"进入kafka容器","index":"1.5"},{"id":"进入所在目录","title":"进入所在目录","index":"1.6"}]},{"id":"kafka管理器","title":"kafka管理器","index":"2","children":[{"id":"安装kafka-manager","title":"安装kafka-manager","index":"2.1"},{"id":"运行kafka-manager","title":"运行kafka-manager","index":"2.2"}]},{"id":"相关链接","title":"相关链接","index":"3"}],"reward":true}